motion: motion (A software motion detector)
motion:
motion: Motion is a program that monitors the video signal from one or more
motion: cameras and is able to detect if a significant part of the picture has
motion: changed; in other words, it can detect motion. Motion is a command
motion: line based tool whose output can be either jpeg, ppm fies or mpeg
motion: video sequences. Motion is the perfect tool for keeping an eye on your
motion: property, keeping only those images that are interesting.
motion:
motion: Packaged by Georgi D. Sotirov <gdsotirov@dir.bg>
motion:
